## 📊 **DATASET STRATEGY MEGA - "Enterprise Intelligence"**

### **🔥 CORE DATASETS (5GB) - "Foundation"**
```yaml
✅ CICIDS2017 (2.4GB): Network flow analysis
  - 2.8M+ network flows, 78 features
  - DDoS, PortScan, Brute Force, Web Attacks, Infiltration, Botnet
  - Primary threat detection engine

✅ NSL-KDD (25MB): Model validation
  - 148K+ connections, 41 pre-engineered features  
  - DoS, R2L, U2R, Probe attacks
  - Proven benchmark for comparison

✅ IP Geolocation (500MB): Geographic mapping
  - Global IP ranges with country/city mapping
  - Known threat actor IP ranges
  - Real-time geographic threat attribution

✅ Threat Intelligence (200MB): IOC feeds
  - Malware signatures and hashes
  - Known malicious domains/IPs
  - Attack patterns and TTPs
```

### **💎 EXPANSION PACK (8GB) - "Professional"**
```yaml
🔄 IoT-23 (2GB): Smart device security
  - 325M+ network flows from IoT devices
  - Mirai, Torii, IoT-specific exploits
  - Smart cameras, thermostats, speakers

🔄 EMBER (600MB): Malware classification
  - 1.1M+ PE files with static analysis features
  - File-based threat detection engine

🔄 SWaT/WADI (1GB): Industrial security
  - Industrial control system data
  - SCADA/HMI communications
  - Cyber-physical attack scenarios

🔄 Credit Card Fraud (50MB): Financial security
  - 284K+ transactions with fraud patterns
  - Financial sector use case demonstration
```

### **🚀 ENTERPRISE PACK (12GB) - "Industry Ready"**
```yaml
⏳ CICAndMal2017 (2GB): Mobile security
  - Android APK analysis
  - Mobile malware family classification

⏳ CSE-CIC-IDS2018 (3GB): Cloud security
  - Cloud infrastructure logs
  - Container security events
  - Kubernetes attack scenarios

⏳ Custom CTI (2GB): Advanced threat intel
  - Live threat feeds integration
  - Custom IOC development
```

### **💾 STORAGE STRATEGY (Total: ~25GB optimized)**
```yaml
Used: ~25GB (leaves 100GB+ for future expansion on 128GB SD)
Compression: LZMA (70% size reduction)
Format: Parquet (3x faster reads)
Processing: Chunked loading, LRU cache
Optimization: Feature selection, model pruning, INT8 quantization
```

