## 🏗️ **ARQUITECTURA LIMPIA PLANEADA - "Next Phase"**

### **📁 ESTRUCTURA PROPUESTA:**
```yaml
backend/
├── app.py                      # Entry point
├── config/                     # Configuration management
├── src/
│   ├── api/v1/                # API Routes (Controllers)
│   │   ├── health.py          # Health checks
│   │   ├── stats.py           # System statistics
│   │   ├── activities.py      # Activity endpoints
│   │   ├── analysis.py        # ML analysis
│   │   ├── geographic.py      # Geographic data
│   │   └── intelligence.py    # Threat intel
│   ├── core/                   # Business Logic (Services)
│   │   ├── services/          # Service layer
│   │   ├── ml/                # ML models and training
│   │   └── utils/             # Utilities
│   └── data/                   # Data Access Layer
│       ├── repositories/      # Repository pattern
│       ├── models/            # Data models
│       └── database/          # DB management
├── tests/                      # Testing framework
└── docs/                       # Documentation
```

### **🎯 PRINCIPIOS DE DISEÑO:**
```yaml
✅ Clean Architecture Layers (Presentation → Business → Data → Infrastructure)
✅ SOLID Principles (Single Responsibility, Open/Closed, etc.)
✅ Design Patterns (Repository, Factory, Observer, Dependency Injection)
✅ Separation of Concerns (API, Business Logic, Data Access)
✅ Testability (Unit tests, Integration tests, Mocking)
✅ Scalability (Microservices ready, Caching, Performance)
```

